<div class="intro">
 <h3> Who are we? </h3>
  <h2> Headed up by the saltiest of sea dogs, and biggest fan of putting flame to vleis, Bossies Chilli co. is a collective of honest, down-to-earth farmers with a taste for delicious and wholesome food and even better sauces.</h2>
  <h2> Organically grown with love on our KZN Midlands farm, our African Birds eye Chillis are carefully blended with other locally-sourced ingredients to deliver the goodness that is our Bossie Chilli sauces. Whether to lather over braai meat, be the star of a cheese and snackboard platter, or simply on a good old fashioned roll or sarmie, Bossies Chilli co. is guaranteed to go down like a home-sick mole!</h2>
</div>
<div class="container2">
  <h3>Our Ama-zing Selection!</h3>
  <div class="cards">
    <% @sauces.each do |sauce| %>
       <div class="card">
           <%= image_tag sauce.photo_url %>
              <h5>
                <%= sauce.name %>
              </h5>
              <p>
                <%= sauce.description %>
                <div class="action">
                <%= link_to "lets go!", sauce_path(sauce), class: "button" %>
                </div>
              </p>
        </div>
      <% end %>
  </div>
</div>
